  <section>
    <h2>Colors</h2>
    <p>Icons inherit <code>currentColor</code> from their parent element. Change the parent's <code>color</code> property to change the icon color.</p>

    <code-block language="html" show-lines label="Icon color inheritance">{{ colorsCode | escape }}</code-block>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>With Buttons</h2>
    <p>Icons work naturally inside buttons. For icon-only buttons, always include an accessible label.</p>

    <code-block language="html" show-lines label="Icons in buttons">{{ buttonsCode | escape }}</code-block>
  </section>

